tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
My wife was having sharp and severe pain in my left waist area. We consulted some doctors in different hospitals who warned us about a kidney stone. However, we came across Dr. Deepthi Raidu  and she correctly pointed out that it was because of an ovarian cyst. She made us understand the situation and the severity with much calmness and as suggested by her, we went on to have a laparoscopic ovarian cystectomy. Surgery went smooth.

I would highly recommend Dr Deepthi Raidu ma‚Äôam for any Gynec related issues. Their expertise in the field and the patience with which they deal with the patients is remarkable.

review:
I visited Dr. Deepthi Raidu on recommendation of my sister in law when I got pregnant. She was very friendly and more concerned than me as I was diagnosed with thyroid and gestational diabetes during my pregnancy. She regularly followed my health status on phone and was always available when required.
I felt personal touch during her treatment and was less stressed as she was always there to take care. I am very grateful to her for gifting me my baby boy without any complications.

review:
Dr Deepthi Raidu , From a doctor to my pregnancy partner to my friend and to a bond I share with her now can‚Äôt be explain in words.
The Journey has not been an easy journey since the conception had many complications but we knew in core of our heart that our baby is in safe hands. Really Thankful.

review:
*** ******* ***** ** * **** ************* ************ Before meeting with Dr. Deepthi Raidu, I have consulted with few other gyne who use to give us very less time.  However Dr Deepthi Raidu always use to answer our list of queries we use to have in each visit  very patiently n calmly and give ..we have of a son and a daughter n way she handled by both deliveries, are just superb..in spite of so many complications she managed so well and gave her support all the time..
Dr Deepthi Raidu prefers to do normal deliveries n tries her best till the end. I had asked her for an C section during my first pregnancy as I was scared abt the delivery pains. But she insisted for trial of vaginal delivery and I delivered my baby by normal Delivery. I would recommend everyone to consult this doctor n get best advice all the time.
